Package lumis.doui.bigdata

DOUI integration with lumis.portal.bigdata.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ISourceBigDataPersister<S extends Source<?>>
    This interface specifies the methods that must be implemented when customizing how a source's data is stored in the portal big data repository.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DouiBigDataUtil
    Utility methods for DOUI with portal big data integration.
    DouiBigDataUtil.DouiBigDataInitObserver
    Portal event observer used to initialize big data for doui usage when repository is initialized.
    DummySourceBigDataPersister<S extends Source<?>>
    A ISourceBigDataPersister implementation that never persist anything.
    TabularSourceBigDataPersister<S extends TabularSource<?>>
    Generic ISourceBigDataPersister for tabular sources.
